    "description": "If you're a passionate Credit Analyst with drive and ambition, CRISIL Consulting Pvt Ltd in Dhanbad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout CRISIL Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nCRISIL Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CRISIL Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
